/steam/apps/3498390/extras/92d4aa6297510955f5380beb7e7c1e37.poster.avif?t=1771685913\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498390/extras/92d4aa6297510955f5380beb7e7c1e37.webm?t=1771685913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498390/extras/92d4aa6297510955f5380beb7e7c1e37.mp4?t=1771685913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
